          <dl class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:mt-20 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col-reverse gap-1">
              <dt class="text-base/7 text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-100">Dispositivos HandHeld reparados con éxito.</dt>
              <dd class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white dark:text-gray-100">3,000+</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col-reverse gap-1">
